<p>The knitted midi dress can easily be styled up or down depending on the occasion. For a more seductive look, it can be worn slightly off the shoulder and paired with heels, but it can equally be worn with tights and boots for a cosy, comfortable look.  </p>

<p>One shopper wrote: 'Not only is it really soft but it keeps you warm! No need to wear a top/shirt underneath!!! Its not too long or short in length and you can alter the neckline to make it higher or more deep. This is a great dress for all occasions (dates, dinner, work etc).'</p>

<p>Another added: 'Drop dead gorgeous. It is comfortable, flattering, nice fabric, beautiful colour. Exactly what you get on the picture... And for this price, an absolute bargain.' </p>

